txt.en: 'Your banners are not fit to fly over Ost Galumar!'
'You and your banners will be hewn this day!'
'You will die a captain to none, fool!'
'This place is ours, and no foolish captain can change that!'
'This place is too well-defended for you!'
'The standard of the Dourhands darkens your grave!'
'The standard of the Dourhands will fly above your corpse!'
'I will not give in to one so weak!'
'Only the standards of the Dourhands will fly over this place!'
